@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-glossary#> .
@prefix bytestar: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-glossary>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Glossary & Roles" ;
  rdfs:comment "Defines CHI, AHI, AHI role taxonomy, and role-to-subsystem bindings." .

### Agents
:Agent a owl:Class .
:Human a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Agent .
:Machine a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Agent .

### Commander & AHI
:CHI a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Human ;
  rdfs:comment "Commander (human) who declares intent and accepts risk." .

:AHI a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Machine ;
  rdfs:comment "Artificial Hyper-Intelligence participant in the Byte* ecosystem." .

### AHI Roles (Planner/Gate/Executor/Governor)
:AHIPlanner  a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :AHI .
:AHIGate     a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :AHI .
:AHIExecutor a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :AHI .
:AHIGovernor a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :AHI .

### Role bindings to subsystems (capabilities)
:operates a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :AHI ; rdfs:range bytestar:Subsystem .

:plansFor  a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :AHIPlanner  ; rdfs:range bytestar:ByteFlow .
:gatesFor  a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :AHIGate     ; rdfs:range bytestar:ByteFlow .
:executesOn a owl:ObjectProperty; rdfs:domain :AHIExecutor  ; rdfs:range bytestar:ByteActor .
:governsVia a owl:ObjectProperty; rdfs:domain :AHIGovernor  ; rdfs:range bytestar:ByteEthos .

### Communication artifacts (glossary links)
:issuesIntent a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :CHI ; rdfs:range :Intent .
:Intent a owl:Class ; rdfs:comment "High-level goal statement consumed by Planner." .